recommend check-in -- the three studies are proposals that touch the roadmap's naming and language-design threads; each names a gated next step (a Glow fleet lap, seating the sixth supplement surface, an explicit non-vane layering in the mapping proposal). Worth Keaton's read on which, if any, graduates from proposal to a seated decision before the next build round.
